<a href="/questions/1019552-in-which-street-or-neighbourhood-does-the">In which street or neighbourhood does the woman live, and does the majority of the book take place? I&#39;m halfway through the book, and there is some location references (Wilmersdorf is a two hour walk, Schöneberg is far) which lead me to think it is based in the north of the city (Pankow?). Does anybody know more?</a>
